        "derivation": "建木为(0,0)；原文先锁窫窳在建木东、狌狌西，按无里数关系最小邻接置(100,0)，并与弱水核心段共享坐标。",
        "sourceUrl": "https://ctext.org/shan-hai-jing/hai-nei-jing/zh\nhttps://ctext.org/shan-hai-jing/hai-nei-nan-jing/zh\nhttps://ctext.org/shan-hai-jing/hai-nei-xi-jing/zhs\nhttps://ctext.org/wiki.pl?chapter=616148&if=gb\nhttps://ctext.org/wiki.pl?chapter=815632&if=gb",
        "geometryType": "point",
